/**
\mainpage

\section sct_about About this Document

\subsection ssct_about_scope_purpose Scope and Purpose

This document describes libAvian, a support library for Infineon radar front
end devices ("Avian" devices). It contains a short overview and a reference
of the classes in libAvian.

\subsection ssct_about_intended_audience Intended Audience
This document is intended for software developers and application engineers who
want to integrate an Avian device into a target application and use libAvian to
control the Avian device and read raw data from it.

